Versions of Mail
================

06-Jul-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix check of local mail queue.

29-Apr-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added i18n support.

06-Nov-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use newer menu system.

26-Jul-2005 (0.3.8)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fixed selection of mailers.

21-May-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Check mtime of inbox before re-counting.

23-Apr-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Require ROX-Lib 2.0.0.

19-Feb-2005 (0.3.7)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Got the "Check mail programs" window working.  Still needs some way of 
editing the entries.

0.3.6
-----
Fix bug which stopped "Select mailer" working.

0.3.5
-----
Fix bug which prevented running the reader.

0.3.4
-----
Updated to make better use of ROX-Lib, such as the standard InfoWin and
stock images in menus.  Also now quits when window/applet closes.

0.3.3
-----
More work on showing number of messages in outgoing queue.

0.3.2
-----
Option to show number of messages in outgoing queue.
Italian translation of AppInfo provided by Yuri Bongiorno.

0.3.1
-----
Fix update to return TRUE, otherwise it never gets called again

0.3.0
-----
Switch to ROX-Lib2 and GTK 2.

0.1.4
-----
Added count of mail messages below icon.

0.1.3
-----
Can run commands to fetch new mail, no UI yet.

0.1.2
-----
Check child processes to avoid zombies where possible.

0.1.1
-----
First released version

-- 
